---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <section class="site-shell hero">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">AI APPLICATIONS · AGENT WORKFLOWS · LOCAL-FIRST</p>
      <h1 class="display-title">把 AI 的能力，放进可控的系统里。</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        我是 yuyukosama2004。我在构建可控、可验证、local-first 的 AI 应用与 Agent
        开发工具，也在这里记录真实的架构取舍与开发实践。
      </p>
      <div class="button-row">
        <a class="button primary" href="/projects">查看项目</a>
        <a class="button" href="https://github.com/yuyukosama2004" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
          访问 GitHub ↗
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="signal-card panel" aria-label="当前关注方向">
      <span class="status"><i></i> currently building</span>
      <dl>
        <div><dt>01</dt><dd>Human-in-the-loop AI</dd></div>
        <div><dt>02</dt><dd>Evidence-backed research</dd></div>
        <div><dt>03</dt><dd>Guarded agent workflows</dd></div>
      </dl>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <section class="site-shell preview-section">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">SELECTED WORK</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">项目不只是代码仓库，而是问题、边界与结果。</h2>
    </div>
    <a class="text-link" href="/projects">浏览全部项目 →</a>
  </section>

  <section class="site-shell placeholder-grid" aria-label="项目预览">
    <article class="panel">
      <span>01 / PRODUCT</span>
      <h3>NovelFlow</h3>
      <p>让 AI 协助长篇创作，但把故事正史的最终决定权留给作者。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="panel">
      <span>02 / RESEARCH</span>
      <h3>GroundedSeek</h3>
      <p>本地优先、证据驱动的 Web Research 服务与 MCP 工作台。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="panel">
      <span>03 / ENGINEERING</span>
      <h3>Guarded Agent Pipeline</h3>
      <p>把多模型编码、外部验证和人工审批组织成可审计的研发流程。</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    display: grid;
    min-height: min(49rem, calc(100vh - 4.5rem));
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.45fr) minmax(18rem, 0.55fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 7vw, 7rem);
    padding-block: 6rem;
  }

  .lede {
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .signal-card {
    padding: 1.35rem;
    transform: rotate(1.5deg);
  }

  .status {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .status i {
    width: 0.55rem;
    height: 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.28rem var(--accent-soft);
  }

  dl {
    margin: 3.5rem 0 0;
  }

  dl div {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2.5rem 1fr;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  dt {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
  }

  dd {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .preview-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-block: 5rem 2rem;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .preview-section h2 {
    max-width: 18ch;
  }

  .text-link {
    color: var(--accent-strong);
    font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .placeholder-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .placeholder-grid article {
    min-height: 20rem;
    padding: 1.4rem;
  }

  .placeholder-grid span {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
  }

  .placeholder-grid h3 {
    margin: 6rem 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .placeholder-grid p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 52rem) {
    .hero {
      min-height: auto;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding-block: 5rem;
    }

    .signal-card {
      transform: none;
    }

    .placeholder-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .placeholder-grid article {
      min-height: 14rem;
    }

    .placeholder-grid h3 {
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 36rem) {
    .preview-section {
      align-items: start;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
